text.__SUMMARY__: Odostomia striata is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Pyramidellidae, the pyrams and their allies.
text.Distribution:
This species occurs in the following locations:
Atlantic
Cobscook Bay
Gulf of Maine
North West Atlantic
USA
